{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place water into mixing bowl and bring to a boil <nobr>5 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/nobr>. Meanwhile, deseed capsicums and cut into strips. Cut larger strips into halves, if desired.","Place Varoma dish into position, add capsicum, secure Varoma lid and steam <nobr>12-14 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/nobr> or until capsicum are tender but still have a slight crunch. Remove Varoma, transfer capsicum into a serving bowl or jar and empty mixing bowl.","Place olive oil, vinegar, cumin and salt into mixing bowl and mix <nobr>20 sec\/speed 6<\/nobr>. Pour dressing over capsicum, combine thoroughly using spatula and allow to cool and marinate for a minimum of 30 minutes. Season to taste and serve as a side dish."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["500 g water","700 g mixed capsicums (e.g. red, green, yellow, orange)","100 g extra virgin olive oil","35 g white wine vinegar","1 tsp ground cumin","3 pinches salt"]}],"id":"r156350","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-Jq8Hk0N4fqI\/XZWaDXMikCI\/AAAAAAAAeVo\/0ZJqNn83L70rDbNF3JjR0butO2EkK3QmgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_vevFEgV0iej_uwM1.png","title":"Marinated capsicum","publishedAt":"2017-05-08T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"1.5 g","fat":"9 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"6 g","calories":"490 kJ \/ 117 kcal"},"usefulItems":"jar","hintsAndTricks":["Serve with fish or grilled meat.<br>- Allow to marinate longer to intensify the flavour.<br>- You can store the capsicums in a clean, sterilised glass jar in the refrigerator for up to 1 week.","Mediterranean style capsicum: After steaming the capsicum, add anchovies, capers, oregano and black olives (all to suit your taste) to the serving bowl."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","55m","6 portions"]}